{"h07bbc7a4g78cbg40baga6a8gf08877427e6b": ["Any sign of those brutes?", "77439e86-3f60-4456-bd55-931e2f45654f", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_AD_ZorruGuard.html", "1f478671-ac19-8c26-7fda-2f4de8d5419a"], "hacf3ab11g6617g474fga29bg65c0c6656d7a": ["No, Zorru. Not a one.", "637d8d68-2a04-409e-a77d-cf31ac9478ee", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_AD_ZorruGuard.html", "fbe8c7a9-b85a-e4a2-23d1-d64e29b8a568"], "h409bd96cg3e98g4d7fgb60bg577d8ec73f65": ["Just wait till you see 'em. Yellow all over. Covered in spots. No noses to speak of.", "77439e86-3f60-4456-bd55-931e2f45654f", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_AD_ZorruGuard.html", "b1d93c99-7d47-b474-c3d7-cbeef9a6b6fd"], "h2e203cfdg42d7g4dceg8526g2056eeec1bd8": ["Those toad-things're coming. I'm sure of it.", "77439e86-3f60-4456-bd55-931e2f45654f", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_AD_ZorruGuard.html", "7a9c320f-c982-0c16-421b-5a43f18cb2d9"], "hd3b3527eg99acg45bdg99eeg6db6844c9118": ["You sure you're remembering right?", "637d8d68-2a04-409e-a77d-cf31ac9478ee", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_AD_ZorruGuard.html", "a7a00e77-d2c3-b8ba-b914-6fe23fdb0417"], "h0ac48075g80b1g488bg9670gf415bcfde0ed": ["I know what I saw. Saw 'em gut Yul. And they'll come gut me too.", "77439e86-3f60-4456-bd55-931e2f45654f", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_AD_ZorruGuard.html", "8d64296d-d13c-c6eb-29be-a0492f1320c4"], "hdf42b193g43bfg4254g863bgfcefa014ae28": ["Be on the lookout for those... things.", "77439e86-3f60-4456-bd55-931e2f45654f", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_AD_ZorruGuard.html", "d57f2005-67fb-53d9-75cf-7ead3fc5b527"], "h5e173883gfc7dg412bgae68g22cf1f8fd031": ["You're tense, Zorru. Maybe you should rest a while.", "637d8d68-2a04-409e-a77d-cf31ac9478ee", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_ThingLikeMe_AD_ZorruGuard.html", "de2ea94d-835e-a47d-75c4-bf541f37e42d"], "h7211dc47g6766g4fefgb77bge35f242c0f4a": ["I won't rest. Not while those yellow freaks are after me.", "77439e